name: Mounts like hills
description:
Mountains are protectors of our village, and all the villages next to us. This part of desert is a bit colder because of the mountains that surrounds it, therefore you can see a lot of gardens and greens  unlike the other cities in desert.
When you don't see a peak, you can find mountains like hills. They make look small, but like a chain they continue until you notice them.
They are as high as the others, they are just far away. Snow is a rare thing but when it comes, you first see it on mountains like hills.
--- 
35mm black and white photography
